<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
  <head>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
    <title>楽アド - 申請について</title>
  </head>
  <body
    style="
      -webkit-text-size-adjust: none;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      color: #74787e;
      font-family: Arial, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, sans-serif;
      height: 100%;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin: 0;
      width: 100% !important;
    "
    bgcolor="#f2f4f6"
  >
    <style type="text/css">
      body {
        width: 100% !important;
        height: 100%;
        margin: 0;
        line-height: 1.6;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        color: #74787e;
        -webkit-text-size-adjust: none;
      }
      @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
        .email-body_inner {
          width: 100% !important;
        }
      }
    </style>

    <table
      class="email-wrapper"
      width="100%"
      cellpadding="0"
      cellspacing="0"
      style="
        box-sizing: border-box;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        width: 100%;
      "
      bgcolor="#f2f4f6"
    >
      <tr>
        <td align="center" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; word-break: break-word">
          <table
            class="email-content"
            width="100%"
            cellpadding="0"
            cellspacing="0"
            style="
              box-sizing: border-box;
              font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
              margin: 0;
              padding: 0;
              width: 100%;
            "
          >
            <tr>
              <td
                class="email-masthead"
                style="
                  box-sizing: border-box;
                  font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
                  padding: 25px 0;
                  word-break: break-word;
                  background-color: #0ea5e9;
                "
                align="center"
                bgcolor="#0ea5e9"
              >
                <a
                  href="{{product_url}}"
                  style="
                    box-sizing: border-box;
                    color: #facc15;
                    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
                    font-size: 24px;
                    font-weight: bold;
                    text-decoration: none;
                  "
                  >{{product_name}}</a
                >
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td
                class="email-body"
                width="100%"
                cellpadding="0"
                cellspacing="0"
                style="
                  -premailer-cellpadding: 0;
                  -premailer-cellspacing: 0;
                  border-bottom-color: #edeff2;
                  border-bottom-style: solid;
                  border-bottom-width: 1px;
                  border-top-color: #edeff2;
                  border-top-style: solid;
                  border-top-width: 1px;
                  box-sizing: border-box;
                  font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
                  margin: 0;
                  padding: 0;
                  width: 100%;
                  word-break: break-word;
                "
                bgcolor="#ffffff"
              >
                <table
                  class="email-body_inner"
                  align="center"
                  width="570"
                  cellpadding="0"
                  cellspacing="0"
                  style="
                    box-sizing: border-box;
                    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
                    margin: 0 auto;
                    padding: 0;
                    width: 570px;
                  "
                  bgcolor="#ffffff"
                >
                  <tr>
                    <td
                      class="content-cell"
                      style="
                        box-sizing: border-box;
                        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
                        padding: 35px;
                        word-break: break-word;
                      "
                    >

    <div style="font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', Arial, sans-serif; color: #2c3e50;">

        <p style="margin: 0 0 20px 0;">{{name}}様</p>

        <p style="margin: 0 0 20px 0;">この度は、楽アドへお見積もり依頼をいただき誠にありがとうございました。</p>

        <p style="margin: 0 0 20px 0;">ご提出いただいた内容を慎重に検討させていただきましたが、誠に恐縮ながら、今回はご希望に沿うことができず、お断りさせていただくこととなりました。</p>

        {{#if reason}}
        <p style="margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><strong>理由：</strong>{{reason}}</p>
        {{/if}}

        <p style="margin: 0 0 20px 0;">ご期待に添えず、大変申し訳ございませんが、何卒ご理解いただけますようお願い申し上げます。</p>

        <p style="margin: 20px 0 0 0;">今後とも何卒よろしくお願いいたします。</p>

        <p style="margin: 20px 0 0 0;">合同会社はと<br>堀田</p>

    </div>
                  
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; word-break: break-word">
                <table
                  class="email-footer"
                  align="center"
                  width="570"
                  cellpadding="0"
                  cellspacing="0"
                  style="
                    box-sizing: border-box;
                    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
                    margin: 0 auto;
                    padding: 0;
                    text-align: center;
                    width: 570px;
                  "
                >
                  <tr>
                    <td
                      align="center"
                      style="
                        box-sizing: border-box;
                        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
                        padding: 35px;
                        word-break: break-word;
                      "
                    >
                      <p
                        style="
                          box-sizing: border-box;
                          color: #bbbfc3;
                          font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
                          font-size: 12px;
                          line-height: 1.5em;
                          margin-top: 0;
                        "
                        align="center"
                      >
                        © 2024 {{product_name}}. All rights reserved.
                      </p>
                      <p
                        style="
                          box-sizing: border-box;
                          color: #bbbfc3;
                          font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
                          font-size: 12px;
                          line-height: 1.5em;
                          margin-top: 0;
                        "
                        align="center"
                      >
                        {{company_name}}
                      </p>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>
